  "updated": 1778758027,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a05b0be0cd3e021d8b3b7a2",
      "text": "中身だけ食べる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778757824,
      "updated": 1778757824
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05b0bf0000000000631012",
      "text": " [貝]とか[蟹]とか[果物]とか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778757824,
      "updated": 1778757859
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05b0d20000000000631015",
      "text": " 肉料理全般そうといえるかも。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778757842,
      "updated": 1778757864
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05b0ef0000000000631017",
      "text": "  肉食動物は、自分と比して小型の動物なら皮ごといく場合があるかもしれない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778757871,
      "updated": 1778757938
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05b1320000000000631018",
      "text": "   人間もトカゲ食べたりするときは多分皮ごとだよね",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778757938,
      "updated": 1778757963
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05b189000000000063101a",
      "text": "   [丸焼き]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778758026,
      "updated": 1778758027
    },
    {
      "id": "6a05b0d80000000000631016",
      "text": " [魚を皮ごと食べますか？]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778757849,
      "updated": 1778757859
    },
